lass="title">参见</h3>   <span>    <ul class="simplelist">     <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link ldap_bind()} - 绑定 LDAP 目录</span></li>    </ul>   </span>  </div>   <div class="up"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/ref.ldap.php">LDAP 函数</a></div></div>
