on">{@link ldap_mod_del_ext()} - Delete attribute values from current attributes</span></li>     <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link ldap_mod_add()} - Add attribute values to current attributes</span></li>     <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link ldap_mod_replace()} - Replace attribute values with new ones</span></li>     <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link ldap_modify_batch()} - Batch and execute modifications on an LDAP entry</span></li>    </ul>   </span>  </div>   <div class="up"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/ref.ldap.php">LDAP 函数</a></div></div>
